      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>The collection consists of annotated typescripts, galley
         and page proofs, and other pre-publication materials relating
         to the book 
         <title render="italic">Letters of a New Market
         Cadet</title>(University of North Carolina Press, 1961) edited
         by historians Robert K. Turner and John G. Barrett. Most of
         the original documents that appear in the book are located in
         the Jaqueline Beverly Stanard Papers VMI Archives (mss
         00083).</p>
      </scopecontent>
